      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine runs strong, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are fully functional. While there are some minor cosmetic signs of normal use, the interior is clean and the car remains a very reliable and attractive option for its next owner.",
