    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior has minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with normal use. The interior is clean with light wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. Mechanically, the car is sound, has been regularly maintained, and all systems are functioning as intended.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the perfect balance of performance and reliability with this meticulously maintained vehicle. Featuring a clean history and a refined interior, this car has been thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our high standards for safety and roadworthiness. It represents an exceptional value for the discerning driver who refuses to compromise on quality. This is more than just a car; it\u2019s a commitment to excellence and a worry-free driving experience.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m finally parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my reliable companion for years, and honestly, it still puts a massive smile on my face every time the engine hums to life. It\u2019s been incredibly well-cared for\u2014always kept tidy and serviced right on time. Sure, it\u2019s got a tiny bit of 'character' here and there from some great road trips, but that just shows it\u2019s a car that\u2019s actually been loved and driven, not just left to sit in a garage. If you\u2019re looking for a smooth, soulful ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! Come by, have a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This machine is a masterclass in mechanical synergy. The power plant delivers exceptionally linear torque thanks to a meticulously calibrated induction system that ensures optimal volumetric efficiency across the rev range. We\u2019ve recently refreshed the subframe bushings and updated the dampers to sharpen turn-in, ensuring the chassis remains composed under high lateral G-loads. The gearbox is crisp, with synchros that exhibit zero hesitation, indicating a drivetrain that has been maintained with exacting tolerances. It\u2019s a turn-key performer dialed in for the purist who values tactile feedback and peak thermal management. No parasitic draws, no vacuum leaks\u2014just pure, unadulterated engineering ready for the apex.",
      "price": 38950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Clean title. Runs perfect. Cold AC. No mechanical issues. Best price on the market. Won't last.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a vehicle; it's a passport to a bygone era of elegance. Draped in a timeless silhouette that captures the golden hour light perfectly, this machine hums with a soulful resonance that modern cars simply cannot replicate. Inside, the cabin greets you with the rich, nostalgic scent of seasoned leather and the tactile charm of analog controls. It possesses a delightful patina\u2014the marks of a life well-lived and many sun-drenched coastal miles enjoyed. Perfect for the driver who prizes spirit and story over sterile perfection, this car is ready to turn every weekend getaway into a cinematic masterpiece.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience the perfect synergy of reliability and refinement with this exceptionally maintained vehicle. Presenting in turn-key condition, this model has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure peak mechanical performance and safety. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a sleek, confident exterior profile, it offers a premium driving experience at a compelling value. This is a rare opportunity to secure a dependable, high-quality vehicle that stands ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve taken really solid care of her, and she\u2019s never let me down on a weekend cruise. She\u2019s got a few tiny signs of being well-loved, but that\u2019s just character in my book! If you\u2019re looking for a reliable, spirited drive that still turns heads, this is the one. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for grabs is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 that has been curated for peak lateral Gs and throttle response. The S54 powerplant maintains rock-solid oil pressure and has undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan seals to ensure optimal cam timing. I\u2019ve already addressed the structural integrity with a full subframe reinforcement kit and powerflex bushings to eliminate any chassis deflection. The cooling stack has been upgraded with a high-capacity aluminum radiator to manage thermal loads during spirited sessions. Shifts are crisp through the ZF 6-speed with a refreshed linkage and weighted selector rod. Riding on dialed-in coilovers with adjustable damping, this machine offers surgical turn-in and follows the apex with zero hesitation. This is a high-strung, driver-focused build that has been maintained with an open-wallet policy regarding its mechanical vitals.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_8",
